lead_paragraph: Carried by samba stars, a supermodel and Prince Albert of Monaco, the Olympic torch made its final journey on Friday from Rio de Janeiro's iconic Christ the Redeemer statue to the Games' opening ceremony amid anti-government protests.

headline.print_headline: Carried by Samba Stars and a Prince, Olympic Torch Nears Ceremony
